{"tid":900034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平讚港澳功臣 點名梁振英何鴻燊等人","createTime":"2018-11-13T02:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T08:00:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55a1b7b125f7393251dd56feb4b652038c42c13a","tid":900034,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:19:49.000Z","msg":"習近平大讚港澳同胞在國家改革開放之初，出錢出力。<br />\n慶祝國家改革開放四十周年港澳代表團昨日最後一日行程入「戲肉」，獲國家主席習近平在北京人民大會堂接見。習主席大讚港澳同胞出錢出力，例如國家改革開放之初，港澳同胞率先響應，踴躍北上投資興業，創造了許多「全國第一」，如內地第一家合資企業、第一條合資高速公路、第一家外資銀行分行、第一家五星級合資飯店等。<br />\n習主席還點名讚賞個別功臣同機構，例如霍英東、何鴻燊在1979年所建的中山溫泉賓館開業後，習主席就親身去參觀過，無論是硬件設備或軟件服務，都是當時內地招待所無法相比的。梁定邦、史美倫幫助創建證券市場有關監管制度，只拿「1元人民幣」的象徵性年薪。前特首梁振英早在1978年已到深圳、上海等地免費舉辦西方土地經濟管理制度的講座，87年又參與編寫了深圳第一份，也是全國第一份土地拍賣中英文標書。<br />\n習主席又讚揚港人善心，例如邵逸夫對內地公益捐款超過100億港元；田家炳為了捐助內地教育慈善事業甚至賣掉自己的別墅，晚年租住公寓。在2010年，青海玉樹發生大地震，香港「愛心義工」黃福榮先生冒著餘震救人，不幸遇難。<br />\n習主席又提到上海虹橋機場引進香港國際機場管理理念，在短期內提升管理水平，奪「世界最快進步機場獎」第一名；北京、廣州、深圳等多個城市的地鐵建設和管理借鑒了香港地鐵的先進經驗。而內地第一支救助飛行隊，正正是在香港飛行服務隊幫助下組建起來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/11/20181112_PO_%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3_FB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F11%2F20181112_PO_%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3_FB.jpg&h=6e1dd825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/11/20181113-PO-%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E3%80%81%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F11%2F20181113-PO-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%2587%258A%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B12.jpg&h=7ea59b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/11/20181113-PO-%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E3%80%81%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F11%2F20181113-PO-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%2587%258A%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B13.jpg&h=b20f9b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171122_EN_%E6%96%B9%E9%80%B8%E8%8F%AF_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171122_EN_%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2580%25B8%25E8%258F%25AF_04.jpg&h=43b9cad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3641872-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AE%9A%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%87%A3-%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA?current_cat=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F3641872-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2587%25A3-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%2587%258A%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%3Fcurrent_cat%3D1&d=53WRbafYR%2FlBXwOwb%2Bn%2BKNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=86a77eba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3641872-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%AE%9A%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%87%A3-%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA?current_cat=1</a>"},{"pid":"640c6f3f0758a765a87f0ae27c8f811b66e67906","tid":900034,"uid":73915,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"可以港獨未？<br />\n<br />\n通常講呢d野，一係要借錢，一係自己就快玩完"},{"pid":"f92369439252435eb5d0091697189f6fb62fd04b","tid":900034,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"比完高帽， 之後就係科水嘅時候"},{"pid":"a16d0bf98aa738